# Email sent to DSpace users when they have works to send to the Orcid Registry but have disable the batch mode
#
#          
#
# See org.dspace.core.Email for information on the format of this file.
#
Subject: TORE - You have works to send to the Orcid Registry

Dear TORE User,

you are recieving this message, because one or more of your publications on TORE 
have been changed and it may be necessary to push it to ORCID again.

Your settings require a manual push.

Please login {0} to send the "works" to the Orcid Registry.
In order to do that, please click on the ORCID tab in your profile and check the synchronization queue.

TORE-Team
